  "title": "Locum Occupational Therapist (Islandwide) - Up to $75/hr #HHW",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assess patients’ physical, mental, and emotional health to develop individualized treatment plans.</li>\n  <li>Provide therapeutic interventions to help patients improve daily living skills and enhance functional abilities.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with doctors, nurses, and other healthcare professionals in the rehabilitation process.</li>\n  <li>Educate patients and their families on strategies to manage and improve functionality.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and document patient progress, adjusting therapy plans as needed.</li>\n  <li>Conduct therapy sessions in both individual and group settings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Occupational Therapy from a recognized institution.</li>\n  <li>Registered with the Allied Health Professions Council (AHPC) of Singapore.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: wendykhoo@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p>Wendy Khoo Hui Wen</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare &amp; Lifescience)</p>\n<p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p>\n<p>Personnel EA License: R1761665</p>",
